result.title: Knuth Cup 2k17
result.content:
Hello Everyone,

We invite you to participate in Knuth Cup 2k17- The Annual Flagship event of Knuth Programming Hub, Jaypee Institute of Information Technology, Noida. There will be some interesting questions of varying difficulties and you can take part in a team of maximum 3 members.

It's going to be a 2-phase contest-Online and Onsite. Online Round will be conducted on 22nd February from 9 P.M. to 1 A.M (IST) on Hackerearth. Top teams will be called for the onsite round which will be held on 25th February 2017.

Online Qualifiers Link : Link

To be eligible for onsite qualification and prizes register here : Link

Note: Contest starts in 2 hours. All the best to all the participants.
